You must have Docker and Docker Compose installed to run this application

We use `make` for this application to speed up develop ease. Below is a list of useful commands.

* run tests by calling `make tests`
* run the PEP8 linter by calling `make lint`
* To build the image do `make build`
* To tear down the application do `make clean`
* To open a developement terminal do `make dev`
* For further information do `make help`
